# Local dev environment overrides.
#
# Copy this file to `dev.env` (git-ignored) and uncomment/edit what you want to change.
# It is sourced by the Makefile

# Image registry used by `make docker-push` and `make chart`.
# Override to build and push dev images under your own registry.
#
#REGISTRY=quay.io/my-user-name
#REGISTRY=ghcr.io/my-user-name

